### Reviews - Generate Cloudinary signature (user)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reviews/cloudinary/sign
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{order_id}}"
}

### Reviews - Get review status for an order
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reviews/orders/{{order_id}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Reviews - Create review for an order item
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reviews
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderItemId": "{{order_item_id}}",
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Sản phẩm đúng mô tả, chất liệu ổn.",
  "images": [
    {
      "url": "https://res.cloudinary.com/.../image/upload/v123/reviews.jpg",
      "publicId": "reviews/userId/orderId/abcd"
    }
  ]
}
